## Pseudocode – Grocery Tracking Program

START

CREATE empty grocery list (dictionary/map)

DISPLAY menu

WHILE user does not choose exit DO
 SHOW options: add item, view items, exit

 IF user selects add item THEN
  GET item name
  IF item exists in list THEN
   INCREASE count by 1
  ELSE
   ADD item with count = 1

 IF user selects view items THEN
  FOR each item in list
   DISPLAY item and count

 IF user selects exit THEN
  END program

END WHILE

END
